platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: It only takes about five minutes to realise just how strange Severed is. But to rescue your family, youre going to have to dive right in, mastering the excellent swipe-based combat, travelling through a magical realm filled with danger, andyeahcollecting some severed limbs. Like we said, its a little weird. But this Apple Design Award winner is also gorgeous, atmospheric and totally memorable.
